title: MDNA EPIX BROADCAST DVD5 NTSC
description:
This file is not my work - I simply shortened the show uploaded by mymdna by editting off the end (their file had a repeat of the show attached on the end after the credits rolled. I then converted the file to a VIDEO_TS file/folder that is ready to burn to a DVD5 (4.7GB. This torrent is in NTSC format (good for North America and some other countries! 

The audio is off-set on purpose by the artist. I didn't like it at first but once you relax into it, the imagery flows and enters the mind in a very cool way - after a few moments I began to really enjoy their unique editting that they did on this project. Highlights for me are when black and white stills are interjected along the way. This video is a work of art folks. So..... enjoy the show!

This is my first torrent. I will seed for a week and hope others will help out after that.

Peace and love to all!
